          "Logan Boese"
        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "Anderson - A Nosferatu whose clan curse has struck to such a degree as to make them of Indeterminate gender. The vampire called Anderson likes to be something of a mystery. They don’t talk about their former life because “It hardly matters”. It goes so far that they often affect different accents, (Some better than others) and speak a smattering of a number of languages. Put simply, their vampire life has been far more kind to them, even with their face and form such as it is now. They were not interested in the opposite sex in life, and now, Blood has replaced even the desire to fit in as such completely. Instead, they can focus on their other interests with full force, and even be rewarded for it. After all, they were always more fond of Watching people rather than interacting with them, and they were masters of their craft. They speak little, and make certain that everything they say is of absolute import and gravitas, that way it fetches the highest price. They’ve made a study of humanity, from body language to sociology and psychology, and it ignited in them a craving to learn more, (one that dovetails nicely with their new craving for their blood,) since then, they’ve really wanted little more than just to Watch, and to sell their information to the highest bidder. They've also made a rather nice \"side\" business, custom making voyeuristic videos of certain people. Naturally, they keep a copy of anything they make, as well as a nice record of the transactions and  orders, (with full knowledge from their customers,) Just so that everyone knows they're armed and prepared to bring people down."
        ],
